dct_title_s: New York City citymap : including Bogota, Englewood, Fairview, Floral Park, Fort Lee ... and adjoining communities, plus index to selective places of interest / H.M. Gousha.
dct_description_sm: Map shows roads, toll and free roads access. Places of interest are listed and located. Panel title. Inset on recto: Map continuation [White Plains vicinity] and  index to streets New Jersey. Ancillary maps on verso: map continued from recto. Staten Island, scale 1:44,352; and index to street New York City and adjacent areas. "10-SF-1583-S" ; "10-SF-1584-S."
dct_publisher_sm: San Jose, CA : H.M. Gousha : Gousha Travel Publications [distributor], 1991.
